A simple online implementation of K-Means clustering for Vectors, with the option to perform agglomerative clustering once all elements have been clustered.

Method Detail

addVector

public int addVector(T value)
Adds value a cluster. The cluster may exist already or a new one may be generated. A unique identifier for the vector being clustered is returned. This identifier is to be used later on to query the cluster to which the value was assigned.
